{"surahDetails":{"id":104,"arabicName":"الهمزة","banglaName":"পরনিন্দাকারী","englishName":"The Traducer","enTranslatedName":"Al-Humazah","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":33,"totalLetters":133,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/104.mp3","totalAyah":9},"surah":{"id":104,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","bangl_text":"প্রত্যেক পশ্চাতে ও সম্মুখে পরনিন্দাকারীর দুর্ভোগ","english_text":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6180.mp3","colorText":"وَيْ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>لٌ ل</tajweed>ِّكُلِّ هُمَزَ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>ةٍ ل</tajweed>ُّمَزَةٍ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","bangl_text":"যে অর্থ সঞ্চিত করে ও গণনা করে","english_text":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6181.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّذِى جَمَعَ مَال<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>اً و</tajweed>َعَدَّدَهُۥ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","bangl_text":"সে মনে করে যে, তার অর্থ চিরকাল তার সাথে থাকবে","english_text":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6182.mp3","colorText":"يَحْسَبُ أَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ مَالَهُ<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>ۥٓ</tajweed> أَخْلَدَهُۥ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","bangl_text":"কখনও না, সে অবশ্যই নিক্ষিপ্ত হবে পিষ্টকারীর মধ্যে।","english_text":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6183.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا‌ۖ لَيُ<tajweed class=iqlab>نۢب</tajweed>َذَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ فِى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْحُطَمَةِ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি জানেন, পিষ্টকারী কি","english_text":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6184.mp3","colorText":"وَم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>رَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ٮٰ</tajweed>كَ مَا <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْحُطَمَةُ <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","bangl_text":"এটা আল্লাহর প্রজ্জ্বলিত অগ্নি","english_text":"It is the fire of Allah, [eternally] fueled","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6185.mp3","colorText":"نَارُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>للَّهِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْمُوقَدَةُ <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","bangl_text":"যা হৃদয় পর্যন্ত পৌছবে।","english_text":"Which mounts directed at the hearts","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6186.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّتِى تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَفْــِٔدَةِ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","bangl_text":"এতে তাদেরকে বেঁধে দেয়া হবে","english_text":"Indeed, Hellfire will be closed down upon them","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6187.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َهَا عَلَيْه<tajweed class=idgham_shafawi>ِم م</tajweed>ُّؤْصَدَةٌ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","bangl_text":"লম্বা লম্বা খুঁটিতে।","english_text":"In extended columns","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6188.mp3","colorText":"فِى عَمَ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>دٍ م</tajweed>ُّمَدَّدَةِۭ <span class=end>٩</span>"}]}}